#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10972
msgid ""
"Power transfer n^γ relative to this frequency step's peak.\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear amplitude, γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude: |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power (and "
"its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to stored "
"electrostatic energy.\n"
"Adjust γ in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"相對於此頻率步階峰值的冪次轉換 n^γ。\n"
"γ = 0.5 可放大微弱區域，γ = 1 為線性振幅，γ = 2 顯示量值平方：|I|² 與每段耗散"
"功率成正比（並透過輻射電阻貢獻其輻射功率），|q|² 則與儲存的靜電能成正比。\n"
"可在動畫對話框中調整 γ。"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10973
msgid "_Power"
msgstr "功率(_P)"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10984
msgid ""
"Logarithmic scale over a user-set range R below the peak.\n"
"Reveals weak detail that linear display hides; adjust R in the animate "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"以使用者設定的範圍 R（低於峰值）呈現對數刻度。\n"
"可顯示線性顯示會隱藏的微弱細節；請在動畫對話框中調整 R。"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10985
msgid "_dB"
msgstr "dB(_D)"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10996
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine transfer: linear below the softening knee k, "
"logarithmic above.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"反雙曲正弦轉換：低於柔化拐點 k 為線性，高於則為對數。\n"
"可在動畫對話框中調整 k。"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10997
msgid "_Asinh"
msgstr "Asinh(_A)"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11008
msgid ""
"μ-law companding transfer: lifts weak detail with bounded compression.\n"
"Adjust the compression in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"μ-law 壓擴轉換：以有限的壓縮提升微弱細節。\n"
"可在動畫對話框中調整壓縮程度。"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11009
msgid "μ-_law"
msgstr "μ-law(_L)"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11020
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational soft-compressor with knee k.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"具拐點 k 的 Reinhard 有理型柔性壓縮器。\n"
"可在動畫對話框中調整 k。"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11021
msgid "_Reinhard"
msgstr "Reinhard(_R)"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11032
msgid ""
